{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for text area component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text area component tokens you want.","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingBlockXl }","        override var sizeMinHeightInput: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._1000 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: TextAreaComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider(","                                            sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens of text area"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSTextArea","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","